{
  "texts": [
    "The next layer is the GRU layer, with 64 units.",
    "A dense layer with 16 neurons is added to overcome the sparsity of GRU's output.",
    "An output layer which is the 3 neurons dense layer, is added for sentiment classification, and 5 neurons dense layer is added for emotion detection, respectively.",
    "The loss function of 'categor-ical_crossentropy' and the 'adam optimizer' is used for training.",
    "The model is then trained using 100 epochs."
  ]
}